015 年翻番达 9.6%，此后保持 10% 以上的比重，2023 年占比达 16.2%。目前该类商品出口金额已快速上升至 570 多亿美元。 越南电子企业协会表示，近 10 年来越南电子行业出口连续排名全国第一，占全国进出口总额的 30% 以上。越工贸部评价认为，越南电子行业近年来的发展主要归功于来自韩国和日本跨国公司在电子元件制造领域的大量投资。 不过越工贸部也称，为了使整个电子及零部件行业，特别是手机行业继续发展，越南国内制造企业必须积极提高竞争力，并在工贸部的支持下挖掘发展潜力。越南超越印度成为全球第二大手机出口国，仅次于中国 - IT 之家"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d25211721f26b672e93787fe0836ac82_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660616770"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy76Slt3dwvZMEAMaCTEwOTA4MTM2MyC875O0BjAAOB1AEnIJNjYwNjE2NzcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1720182984.18246", "card_id": "Q_660462759", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 52}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "电子书与纸质书，到底哪个更适合你？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在数字化阅读日益普及的今天，纸质书与电子书在阅读体验、知识吸收效率、以及对环境的影响等方面有哪些具体的差异？如何根据个人需求和习惯选择最合适的阅读方式？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-174a60a654417a4352be6875b60320a6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660462759"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iy76Slt3dwvZMEAMaCTEwOTA0NzMxMSCcxoq0BjAAOD5AE3IJNjYwNDYyNzU5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1720182984.20366", "card_id": "Q_657639060", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "五十岁以上的跑者，跑什么配速合适？你平时跑步的配速是多少呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c1534f877ce44a3be24e0687